that science and technology play for the development and socio-
economic integration of the continent.
</P>
<P>
"Awarding the best African inventors/innovators gold medals is
a token of international recognition of the creativity of African
researchers," he added.
</P>
<P>
Members of the jury were drawn from various African countries.
The award will be given next June. enditem

