<HEADLINE> World Champion to Run in London Marathon </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, April 3 (Xinhua) -- World champion Manuela Machado of
Portugal has decided to run in next week's London Marathon,
organizers announced here on Thursday.
</P>
<P>
The Portuguese had made a late decision to run a spring
marathon and has chosen to return to London on April 13 where she
will take on defending champion Liz McColgan of Britain.
</P>
