open a new chapter in the history of the bilateral relations and
ties between the two armed forces, hoping that such a friendly and
cooperative relations will be promoted from generation to
generation.
</P>
<P>
Chavalit, who is also defense minister, said that the relations
between the two armed forces of the two countries have witnessed
continuous development, and he is happy to exchange views on
developing ties between the two armed forces and on regional
issues.
</P>
<P>
Fu Quanyou, Chief of General Staff of the Chinese People's
Liberation Army, and other senior officials were present at the
meeting.
