posted 375,126 cases (about 3.4 million liters) last year.
</P>
<P>
According to statistics by the Excise Department of the Thai
Finance Ministry, the United States exported 291,885 cases (about
2.6 million liters) of wine to Thailand, ranking second, followed
by Australia which sell 157,518 cases to Thailand in the year.
