<TEXT>
<P>
ATHENS, April 2 (Xinhua) -- Greek Prime Minister Costas Simitis
today agreed to grant 80 million U.S. dollars in urgent economic
assistance to Albania to help the crisis-ridden country out of
difficulties.
</P>
<P>
