about that order would soon be restored in the country.
</P>
<P>
Jan Graf de Marchand et d'Ansemburg, who led an 11-member
delegation from the EU to assess the situation in the Balkan
nation, told reporters before leaving here that Albania's
national reconciliation government has brought the country hope.
</P>
