general election after violence erupted in the country last month
following the collapse of pyramid investment schemes.
</P>
<P>
D'Ansemburg also said the sinking of an Albanian refugee boat
heading for Italy last week in which some 80 people are estimated
to have died, will not affect the EU's relations with Albania.
</P>
<P>
The EU has provided Albania with two million ecus (about two
million U.S. dollars) in relief aid to help get the country's
economy back on its feet.
</P>
<P>
The EU delegation arrived here on March 26 for talks with
Albania's all parties concerned about aid plans. 
