<TEXT>
<P>
SAN JOSE, April 2 (Xinhua) -- A Dutch frigate with 165 crew
members on board will pay a three-day visit to Costa Rica starting
Friday, Frans Vantlaren, Dutch ambassador to the Central American
country said here today.
</P>
